<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th" class="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GAME STORAGE - ข่าวสาร รีวิวเกม และเกมมิ่งเกียร์</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- Google Fonts: Prompt -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Prompt:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: { prompt: ['Prompt', 'sans-serif'] },
                    colors: {
                        brand: {
                            dark: '#0d0f12',
                            card: '#161920',
                            accent: '#00ff88', // สีเขียวเนออน
                            hot: '#ff4757',    // สีแดงดีลเด็ด
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-brand-dark text-gray-200 font-prompt min-h-screen flex flex-col">

    <!-- NAVIGATION BAR -->
    <nav class="bg-brand-card/90 backdrop-blur border-b border-gray-800 sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-wider text-white">GAME <span class="text-brand-accent">STORAGE</span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-6 text-sm font-medium">
                <a href="#hero" class="hover:text-brand-accent transition">ข่าวเด็ด</a>
                <a href="#reviews" class="hover:text-brand-accent transition">รีวิวเกม</a>
                <a href="#hardware" class="hover:text-brand-accent transition">เกมมิ่งเกียร์</a>
                <a href="#deals" class="hover:text-brand-accent transition">แจกเกมฟรี/ดีล</a>
                <a href="#community" class="hover:text-brand-accent transition">พูดคุย</a>
            </div>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/GAMESTORAGE" target="_blank" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-semibold transition">
                ติดตามบน Facebook
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 space-y-16 flex-1">

        <!-- SECTION 1: HERO HIGHLIGHTS -->
        <section id="hero" class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <!-- Main Banner -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-2 relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden group bg-brand-card border border-gray-800">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542751371-adc38448a05e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Main News" class="w-full h-[380px] object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-dark via-brand-dark/40 to-transparent p-6 flex flex-col justify-end">
                    <span class="bg-brand-accent text-black font-bold text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full w-max mb-2">Editor's Choice • 9.5/10</span>
                    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">รีวิวฉบับเต็มเกมระดับ AAA แห่งปี สมการรอคอยหรือแค่กระแส?</h1>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm line-clamp-2">เจาะลึกระบบเกมเพลย์ กราฟิก และประสิทธิภาพบน PC ก่อนที่คุณจะตัดสินใจกดซื้อ...</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Sub Banner -->
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                <div class="bg-brand-card border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-xl flex gap-4 items-center hover:border-brand-accent/50 transition">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550745165-9bc0b252726f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=200&q=80" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-lg object-cover">
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-xs text-brand-accent font-semibold">ข่าวด่วน</span>
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-white hover:text-brand-accent cursor-pointer">เปิดตัวการ์ดจอรุ่นใหม่ สเปกแรงทะลุหลอด!</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">2 ชั่วโมงที่แล้ว</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-brand-card border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-xl flex gap-4 items-center hover:border-brand-accent/50 transition">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1612287230202-1ff1d85d1bdf?auto=format&fit=crop&w=200&q=80" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-lg object-cover">
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-xs text-brand-hot font-semibold">Console</span>
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-white hover:text-brand-accent cursor-pointer">อัปเดตเฟิร์มแวร์ใหม่ เพิ่มโหมดประหยัดพลังงาน</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">5 ชั่วโมงที่แล้ว</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 2: GAMING GEAR & HARDWARE REVIEWS -->
        <section id="hardware">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-6">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-6 bg-brand-accent rounded-full"></span>
                        Gaming Gear & Hardware
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">ป้ายยาอุปกรณ์จัดโต๊ะคอมและการ์ดจอตัวแรง</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <!-- Card 1 -->
                <div class="bg-brand-card border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-gray-700 transition">
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-brand-accent rounded">Headset</span>
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1546435770-a3e426bf472b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" class="w-full h-40 object-cover rounded-lg my-3">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-white text-base">Wireless Gaming Headset Pro</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">เกรดแข่ง ตัดเสียงรบกวนเยี่ยม เสียงเบสแน่นสะใจ</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-gray-800 flex justify-between items-center">
                        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">฿4,290</span>
                        <button class="bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-brand-accent/30 hover:bg-brand-accent hover:text-black transition">เช็กราคา</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Card 2 -->
                <div class="bg-brand-card border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-gray-700 transition">
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-brand-accent rounded">Keyboard</span>
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1587829741301-dc798b83add3?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" class="w-full h-40 object-cover rounded-lg my-3">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-white text-base">Custom Mechanical Keyboard 75%</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">ฟีลลิ่งการพิมพ์นุ่มนวล ไฟ RGB ปรับแต่งได้อิสระ</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-gray-800 flex justify-between items-center">
                        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">฿3,590</span>
                        <button class="bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-brand-accent/30 hover:bg-brand-accent hover:text-black transition">เช็กราคา</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Card 3 -->
                <div class="bg-brand-card border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-gray-700 transition">
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-brand-accent rounded">GPU</span>
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591488320449-011701bb6704?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" class="w-full h-40 object-cover rounded-lg my-3">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-white text-base">Graphics Card 16GB VRAM</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">การ์ดจอรุ่นคุ้มค่า เล่นเกมปรับสุดได้ลื่นๆ 4Kสบาย</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-gray-800 flex justify-between items-center">
                        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">฿24,900</span>
                        <button class="bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-brand-accent/30 hover:bg-brand-accent hover:text-black transition">เช็กราคา</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 3: GAME REVIEWS & PLATFORMS -->
        <section id="reviews">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
                <span class="w-2 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></span>
                คลังรีวิวเกม (Game Reviews)
            </h2>
            <!-- Filter Tabs -->
            <div class="flex gap-2 border-b border-gray-800 pb-3 mb-6 overflow-x-auto text-xs">
                <button class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-accent text-black font-bold">ทั้งหมด</button>
                <button class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-card text-gray-400 hover:text-white">PC</button>
                <button class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-card text-gray-400 hover:text-white">PlayStation</button>
                <button class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-card text-gray-400 hover:text-white">Nintendo Switch</button>
            </div>
            <!-- Game Grid -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-brand-card rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-800">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1538481199705-c710c4e965fc?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" class="h-48 w-full object-cover">
                    <div class="p-3">
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-blue-400 font-semibold">Action RPG</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-sm truncate">Fantasy Open World</h4>
                        <div class="mt-2 text-xs text-brand-accent font-bold">★ 8.8 / 10</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-brand-card rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-800">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511512578047-dfb367046420?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" class="h-48 w-full object-cover">
                    <div class="p-3">
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-red-400 font-semibold">FPS</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-sm truncate">Cyber Tactics 2026</h4>
                        <div class="mt-2 text-xs text-brand-accent font-bold">★ 9.0 / 10</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-brand-card rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-800">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579373903781-fd5c0c30c4cd?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" class="h-48 w-full object-cover">
                    <div class="p-3">
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-yellow-400 font-semibold">Co-Op</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-sm truncate">Space Explorer</h4>
                        <div class="mt-2 text-xs text-brand-accent font-bold">★ 7.5 / 10</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-brand-card rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-800">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560253023-3ec5d502959f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" class="h-48 w-full object-cover">
                    <div class="p-3">
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-purple-400 font-semibold">Horror</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-sm truncate">Silent Shadows</h4>
                        <div class="mt-2 text-xs text-brand-accent font-bold">★ 8.2 / 10</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 4: DEALS & FREE GAMES -->
        <section id="deals" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-900/30 to-brand-card border border-red-500/30 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-2xl">🔥</span>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Game Storage Deals & แจกเกมฟรี</h2>
                </div>
                <span class="text-xs bg-brand-hot text-white font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded">อัปเดตสัปดาห์นี้</span>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-black/40 border border-gray-700/50 p-4 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-between">
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-green-400 border border-green-400/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">FREE GAME</span>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-white text-sm mt-1">Epic Games Store</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">หมดเขตแจก 28 ก.ค. นี้</p>
                    </div>
                    <button class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-black text-xs font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">กดรับเกม</button>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-black/40 border border-gray-700/50 p-4 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-between">
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-brand-hot border border-red-500/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">STEAM SALE -75%</span>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-white text-sm mt-1">Summer Sale Campaign</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">ลดราคาเกมดังกว่า 1,000+ เกม</p>
                    </div>
                    <button class="bg-brand-hot hover:bg-red-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">ลายเซ็นดีล</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 5: COMMUNITY & TRENDS -->
        <section id="community">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
                <span class="w-2 h-6 bg-purple-500 rounded-full"></span>
                กระทู้เด็ด & ประเด็นร้อน
            </h2>
            <div class="bg-brand-card border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-4 divide-y divide-gray-800">
                <div class="py-3 flex justify-between items-center hover:bg-gray-800/30 px-2 rounded-lg cursor-pointer">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="text-gray-500 font-bold text-sm">01</span>
                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-200">ทำไมสายจัดสเปกคอมช่วงนี้ถึงแนะนำให้เพิ่ม RAM เป็น 32GB?</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">💬 128 ความเห็น</span>
                </div>
                <div class="py-3 flex justify-between items-center hover:bg-gray-800/30 px-2 rounded-lg cursor-pointer">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="text-gray-500 font-bold text-sm">02</span>
                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-200">สรุปดราม่าค่ายเกมดัง ปรับนโยบายเติมเงิน กระทบสายฟรีอย่างไรบ้าง</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">💬 89 ความเห็น</span>
                </div>
                <div class="py-3 flex justify-between items-center hover:bg-gray-800/30 px-2 rounded-lg cursor-pointer">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="text-gray-500 font-bold text-sm">03</span>
                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-200">แนะนำ 5 จอมอนิเตอร์ 144Hz งบไม่เกิน 5,000 บาท เล่นเกม FPS ลื่นตา</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">💬 204 ความเห็น</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <!-- SECTION 6: FOOTER & SOCIAL HUB -->
    <footer class="bg-brand-card border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 py-8">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
            <div>
                <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">GAME <span class="text-brand-accent">STORAGE</span></span>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">พื้นที่อัปเดตข่าวสาร รีวิวเกม และเกมมิ่งเกียร์สำหรับเกมเมอร์ตัวจริง</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/GAMESTORAGE" target="_blank" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-sm">Facebook Page</a>
                <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-sm">ติดต่องาน/โฆษณา</a>
                <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-sm">Privacy Policy</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 text-center text-xs text-gray-600 mt-6">
            © 2026 GAME STORAGE. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
